---
import { Terminal, Check, Copy } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="developer-docs" class="py-16 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-brand-border/80 transition-colors">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-blue/10 dark:bg-brand-accent/10 border border-brand-blue/30 dark:border-brand-accent/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-accent">
        <Terminal class="w-6 h-6" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="dev_title">基于 DeepFlow 进行二次开发</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="dev_description">DeepFlow 的主进程和渲染进程全部基于 TypeScript 开发。它提供了完美的 TS 类型镜像支持（electron/types.ts ↔ src/types/），无论您是想扩展底层工具、外接企业 MCP 服务器还是修改 Zustand 的 12 个持久化 Store，我们都已准备好了完善的基础设施。</p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue/10 dark:bg-brand-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-accent mt-0.5"><Check class="w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true" /></div>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300" data-i18n="dev_check1">Vitest 前后端覆盖率门槛，代码更稳健</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue/10 dark:bg-brand-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-accent mt-0.5"><Check class="w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true" /></div>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300" data-i18n="dev_check2">严格的 CSP 内容安全限制与沙箱锁保证主进程安全</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-7">
      <div class="code-dark-box border border-slate-700 dark:border-brand-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden font-mono text-xs shadow-xl">
        <div class="bg-brand-black px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-800 dark:border-brand-border flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-slate-400" data-i18n="dev_titlebar">快速克隆并启动开发</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-600 font-bold" data-i18n="dev_titlebar_type">TypeScript / Vite</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-2" data-i18n="dev_step1_comment">// 1. 克隆底层核心仓库</p>
            <div class="bg-brand-black/60 p-3 rounded border border-slate-700 dark:border-brand-border flex items-center justify-between group">
              <span class="text-brand-accent">git clone https://github.com/yth1120/DeepFlow.git</span>
              <button data-copy-text="git clone https://github.com/yth1120/DeepFlow.git" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors p-1 rounded hover:bg-slate-700/50" aria-label="复制命令" title="点击复制"><Copy class="w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true" /></button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-2" data-i18n="dev_step2_comment">// 2. 创建本地开发环境变量配置</p>
            <div class="bg-brand-black/60 p-3 rounded border border-slate-700 dark:border-brand-border flex items-center justify-between group">
              <span class="text-slate-300">cp .env.example .env</span>
              <button data-copy-text="cp .env.example .env" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors p-1 rounded hover:bg-slate-700/50" aria-label="复制命令" title="点击复制"><Copy class="w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true" /></button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-2" data-i18n="dev_step3_comment">// 3. 安装依赖并启动 Electron 联动调试开发</p>
            <div class="bg-brand-black/60 p-3 rounded border border-slate-700 dark:border-brand-border">
              <span class="text-slate-300 block">npm install</span>
              <span class="text-brand-accent block">npm run electron:dev</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('[data-copy-text]').forEach((btn) => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      const text = btn.getAttribute('data-copy-text');
      if (!text) return;
      try {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
        const iconEl = btn.querySelector('svg');
        if (iconEl) {
          const orig = iconEl.outerHTML;
          iconEl.outerHTML = '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-check"><path d="M18 6 7 17l-5-5"/><path d="m22 10-7.5 7.5L13 16"/></svg>';
          setTimeout(() => { const r = btn.querySelector('svg'); if (r) r.outerHTML = orig; }, 1500);
        }
      } catch {}
    });
  });
</script>
